For International ispell,
ispell-3.4.00 was released Feb 9 2015, is the latest as of Sep 2016.
is the latest as of 

Ispell 3.2
http://fmg-www.cs.ucla.edu/fmg-members/geoff/ispell.html

# Do all this on geyer
cd ~/tmp
wget http://fmg-www.cs.ucla.edu/geoff/tars/ispell-3.2.06.tar.gz
tar zxvf ispell-3.2.06.tar.gz
cd ispell-3.2.06
# For USG (System V) systems such as Linux:
cp -p local.h.samp local.h
## Edit local.h:
#  -#undef USG		/* Define on System V or if term.c won't compile */
#  +#define USG		/* Define on System V or if term.c won't compile */
## And add the end:
#  #define LANGUAGES "{american,MASTERDICTS=american.med+,HASHFILES=americanmed.hash,EXTRADICT=/usr/dict/words}"
#  #define EQUAL_COLUMNS
#  #define SORTPERSONAL 10000
#  #define MAX_SCREEN_SIZE 24
make
sudo make install

